        <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>
        <Description>A .NET Blazor Razor Class Library (BRCL) that include Navigation menu, PageContainer, Pagination, Sort, Search, Banner, Footer and other helpful components and classes.

